  <description>
    <p>
      **NOTE: This wrapper is not verified by, affiliated with, or supported by The Pixel Guys.**
    </p>
    <p>
      Welcome to Cubyz !
    </p>
    <p>
      An open-world adventure game where creativity knows no bounds! Explore, build, and shape your
      own world in this open source project.
    </p>
    <p>It has a bunch of interesting/unique features such as: <ul>
        <li>
          Unique Gameplay → Experience a one-of-a-kind gameplay that combines creativity and
      strategy.
        </li>
        <li>Level of Detail → This enables far view distances.</li>
        <li>
          Cubic Chunks → Explore a world built from cubic chunks, allowing for infinite
          exploration in all directions.
        </li>
        <li>
          Procedural Crafting → You can craft anything you want, and the game will figure out
          what kind of tool you tried to make.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </description>
